---
title: Moroccan Beef & Chickpea Filo Pie with Coconut Sauce & Roasted Veggies
description: You don’t need to visit a bakery to try out this beef and chickpea pie. You can easily make it at home and eat it piping hot from the oven. Enjoy the pop of coconut flavours in the sauce and the roast veggies.
